𝐭𝐡𝐫𝐞𝐞 widely used kubernetes deployment strategies that ensures smooth and efficient updates in production.🔄

☑️𝐑𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐥𝐨𝐲𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭: It gradually replaces old versions with new ones to ensure near zero downtime.
☑️𝐂𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐫𝐲 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐥𝐨𝐲𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭: This type tests by sending small percentage of traffic to the new version before full rollout.
☑️𝐁𝐥𝐮𝐞-𝐆𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐧 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐥𝐨𝐲𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭: Maintains two environments and switch traffic between them for seamless updates.

Whether you are looking to ensure 𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐨 𝐝𝐨𝐰𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐦𝐞 or optimize your update process, these strategies will help you achieve your goal.